      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Hamburg, 5 January 1853 ¶ Esteemed Sir, ¶  ¶ When I received the Australian Dodonaeae ¶  ¶ back towards the end of September with the request to also send you the ones collected by Preiss, I did not e...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">M53.01.05</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">From<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Wilhelm Sonder to<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Diederich von Schlechtendal</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="Normal" style="hyphenate: false; " xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     </seg>MS not seen; extracted from Tkach, Neubauer &amp; Roser (2022), Brief<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>12.</p>
               </note>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">Hamburg d. 5 Janr. 53<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Hochgeehrter Herr!</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Als ich gegen Ende September die austral.</seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Dodonaeen<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">zurückerhielt</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">mit der Aufforderung, Ihnen auch</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">die von Preiss gesammelten zukommen zu lassen, erwartete ich nicht,</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">dass zu der Ausführung dieses Ihres</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">Wunsches so viel Zeit gehören werde.</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">Theils waren es die zahlreichen Geschäfte</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">die mich abhielten, theils das Aufsuchen</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">der gewünschten Pflanzen, die bei dem</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">häufigen Gebrauche hinter die M</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">ü</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">ller’schen gerathen sind, und die selbst</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">heute noch nicht alle mitkommen,</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">endlich aber vermutete ich einen Tag</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">nach dem anderen die Sendung von</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">Müller,</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>die in England liegen geblie</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">ben war und die Ihnen etwas zum</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">Drucken für die Linnaea bringen</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">sollte. Sie erhalten also noch nicht</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">alle Dodonaeen, 2 oder 3 Arten</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">sind noch versteckt, müssen sich aber</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">in den nächsten Tagen auffinden, da ich</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">nun auch ein Dutzend Packete durchzusehen habe; sie sollen bald nachfolgen.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Wenn Sie den Druck des Müller’schen<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Manuskripts<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>bald vornehmen lassen<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>können, so wäre es mir in sofern lieb,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>als ich in Anfang März Gelegenheit<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>habe, eine Kiste nach Australien zu senden.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Wie interessant Müller’s<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Pflanzen jetzt<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>werden, ersehen Sie aus den beiliegenden<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Beschreibungen, die wunderschön aufgelegten<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Exemplare sind alle in meinen<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Händen.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Mit Einschluss<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>der auf Vandiemensland gesammelten Arten beläuft sich nach meiner oberflächlichen Annahme die Zahl der geschickten auf fast 1500 Species.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Und was ist bei dem wirklich ausserordenlichen Eifer Müller’s<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>nicht noch zu erwarten. Vielleicht ist Müller jetzt schon in<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Port Philipp, da ihm die Vegetation von Adelaide<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>u dem Murray<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>nicht Neues genug mehr bot.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich habe jetzt wirklich angefangen<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>die ganze Sammlung kritisch durchzunehmen, hätte aber gerne noch Hülfe<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>dabei. An Bentham habe ich wegen der<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>sehr zahlreichen Acacien u Leguminosen<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>geschrieben, Lindley wird die Orchideen<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>nachsehen (weil Müller es wünscht, sonst hätte<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>ich sie Reichenbach jr. geschickt), Fenzl habe<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>ich auch aufgefordert.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Wenn ich den nur<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>noch 1 oder 2 Mitarbeiter hätte, so sollte<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>das ganze bald fertig sein. Mit den zahlreichen und manches neue enthaltenden<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Compositeen</hi>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>bin ich beinahe zu Ende, ich<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>denke Ihnen in 14 Tagen bis 3 Wochen<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>die Aufzählung derselben zuzusenden, ich<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>möchte gerne, dass nach dem Druck des<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Müller’schen Manuskript meine Enumeratio<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>sogleich folgen könnte.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Müller hat ausser der Calotis cuneifolia,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>noch die erinacea Steetz, die scapigera Hook.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>und 3 oder 4 andere gesammelt.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Ueber<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Ihre Gnaphalia<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>210 u 211 werden Sie näheres<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>bei mir finden;<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Ihr Aster? Behrii187<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>ist<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Eurybiopsis gracilis Hook. fil, welche<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Müller u wohl mit Recht unter dem Namen<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>E. hookeri mit E. scabrida Hook. zusammenzieht.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">Zwiebelgewächse sind seit längerer Zeit</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">nicht aus Südafrika angekommen und wohl</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">deshalb, weil wir die letzten von Zeyher</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">geschickten n</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">icht gut verkaufen konnten. Man<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">hat</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>hier die Erfahrung gemacht, dass</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>diese</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">Zwiebeln sich nicht lange halten, sie werden</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">immer kleiner und gehen allmälig aus.</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">Wollen Sie übrigens deshalb Zeyher</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">schreiben, so will ich den Brief gerne einlegen oder</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>b</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">efördern, mit Dr. Pappe werden Sie nichts anfangen. Zeyher hat im vorigen Monate wieder</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Sämereien geschickt,</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">Drège läss</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">t glaube ich, jetzt die</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Verzeichnisse</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">drucken. Auch M</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">ü</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">ller hat Saamen aus</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">Australien geschickt, die ich auch an Drège</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">gegeben habe.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Lindley’s Folia orchidacea werden Sie<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>gesehen haben, das Werk ist prächtig gehalten.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Es wäre zu wünschen, dass<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Reichenb. fil.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>sich bemühte, sich an Lindley anzuschliessen; unsere Gärtner hier bei Hamburg sagen,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>die Reichenbach’schen Diagnosen seien ihnen<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>zu weitläufig u nicht so verständlich als die Lindleys’schen.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Dr. M</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">ü</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">ller möchte gerne 12 Abdrucke seiner Arbeit haben,</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">er meint, er könne</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">durch Ve</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">rtheilung einiger Exemplare an<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">dortige gewichtige Leute seine botanischen</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">Bestrebungen fördern.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Das Päckchen für Dr. Areschoug wird<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>erst mit dem ersten Frühlingsschiffe abgehen.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Areschoug ist aber selbst Schuld daran, denn<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>er antwortete mir so spät auf meinen<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Brief, sodass<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>ich die Kiste mit Spongien<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>nicht<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>mehr p.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Dampfschiff expedieren konnte. Areschoug<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>beabsichtigt über die Spongien zu arbeiten.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Wir haben hier viel u schönes Material<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>davon, das ich<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>ihm übergeben will. Schade dass<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>kein Deutscher sich bis jetzt dazu<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>hergegeben hat, bei der Arbeit glaube ich<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>sind Loorbeeren zu erringen.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">Ich wollte<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">eine kleine Bemerkung zu</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">dem M</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">ü</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">ller’schen Manuskripte hinzufügen, habe</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">es aber vergessen, und nun ist das Packet</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">versiegelt. Möchten Sie nicht als</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">Anmerkung dazu setzen, dass diese neuen</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">Pflanzen einen Theil der an mich gesandten</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">käuflichen<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">M</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">ü</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">ller’schen Sammlungen ausma</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">chen und<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">dass eine Aufzählung sämtlicher Arten folgen werde.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Die beigelegte Dodonaea<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>von Sieber finde ich nicht in DCandolle.</p>
            <p rend="Normal"
               style="hyphenate: false; text-align: end; margin-bottom: 0.1666in; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Mit vorzüglicher Hochachtung<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="Normal"
               style="hyphenate: false; text-align: end; margin-bottom: 0.1666in; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Ihr<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="Normal"
               style="hyphenate: false; text-align: end; margin-bottom: 0.1666in; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">ergebenster<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">W. Sonder<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Sie wundern sich<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>vielleicht, dass ich zwei der Mueller’schen Compositen<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>durchstrichen habe; dieselben sind aber neuerdings von Asa Gray<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>in Hooker’s London Journal beschrieben.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Hamburg, 5 January 1853</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Esteemed Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>When I received the Australian Dodonaeae<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>back towards the end of September with the request to also send you the ones collected by Preiss, I did not expect that it would take so much time to fulfil your wish.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Partly it was the numerous business matters that prevented me from doing so, partly it was the search for the desired plants, which have fallen behind Mueller's due to their frequent use and which even today do not all come<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>along;<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>but finally I<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>expected one day after the other that Mueller's consignment, which had been left behind in England and which was supposed to bring you something to print for the Linnaea.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Therefore you do<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>not yet receive all the Dodonaeae, 2 or 3 species are still hidden but must be found in the next few days as I now have<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>but<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>a dozen packages to look through; they should follow soon.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>If you can have Mueller's manuscript printed soon, I would appreciate it, as I will have the opportunity to send a box to Australia at the beginning of March.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>You will see how interesting Mueller's plants are now becoming from the enclosed<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>descriptions;<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the beautifully presented specimens are all in my hands.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Including the species collected in Van<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Diemen's<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Land, my superficial assumption is that the number of species<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>sent<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>amounts to almost 1500. And what else is not to be expected with Mueller's truly extraordinary zeal. Perhaps Mueller is already in Port Phillip, as the vegetation of Adelaide and the Murray no longer offered him enough new things.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have now really started to go through the whole collection critically, but would still like some help.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I have written to Bentham about the very numerous Acacias and Leguminosae. Lindley will attend to<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the orchids (because Mueller wants it, otherwise I would<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>have sent them to Reichenbach jr.).<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>have also asked Fenzl.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText" style="hyphenate: false; " xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See Sonder to Fenzl 15 November 1952, 27 December 1852.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>If I only had 1 or 2 more collaborators, the whole thing would be finished soon. I am almost finished with the numerous and many new<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">composites,</hi>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I think I will send you the list of them in 14 days to 3 weeks.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I would like<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>that<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>my<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>listing<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>could<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>follow immediately after the printing of Mueller's manuscript.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Apart from<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Calotis cuneifolia</seg>, Mueller has also collected<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">erinacea</seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Steetz,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">scapigera</seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Hook. and 3 or 4 others. You will find more details about your<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Gnaphalia</seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>210 and 211 in my contribution; your<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Aster</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">? b</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">ehrii</seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>is<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Eurybiopsis gracilis</seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Hook. fil, which Mueller<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>probably<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>rightly combines with<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">E. scabrida</seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Hook. under the name<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">E. hookeri</seg>.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Bulbous plants have not arrived from South Africa for a long time and probably because we could not sell the last ones sent by Zeyher very well. It has been our experience<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>here<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>that these bulbs do not last long, they become smaller and smaller and gradually die out.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>If, by the way, you want to write to Zeyher about this, I will gladly insert or forward the letter; you won't get anywhere with Dr. Pappe. Zeyher<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>sent seeds again last month, and I believe Drège is now having the lists printed. Mueller has also sent seeds from Australia, which I have also given to Drège.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>You will have seen Lindley's<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Folia orchidacea</seg>, which is a splendid work. It would be desirable for Reichenbach fil. to make an effort to follow Lindley; our gardeners here in Hamburg say that Reichenbach's diagnoses are too long-winded<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>for them and not as comprehensible as Lindley's.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Dr. Mueller would like to have 12 copies of his work; he thinks he could promote his botanical endeavours by distributing a few examples<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>to important<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">people there.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The parcel for Dr. Areschoug will only leave with the first spring ship.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>But it is Areschoug's own fault, because he answered my letter so late that I was unable to send the box of sponges<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>per steamship. Areschoug intends to work on the sponges.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>We have a lot of beautiful material<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>of<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>them here, which I want to hand over to him. It's a pity that no German has so far<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>anything to<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>do<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>with them, I think there are laurels to be won in this work.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I wanted to add a small remark to Mueller's manuscript but I forgot, and now the package is sealed. Would you not like to add as a note that these new<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>plants make up a part of the Mueller collections sent to me<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>for sale<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>and that a list of all species will follow.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I do not find the enclosed<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Dodonaea</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>of<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Sieber in de<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Candolle.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">With sincere esteem,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>most devoted</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>W. Sonder<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="line-height: 0.1944in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">You may be surprised that I have crossed out two of<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Mueller composites; however, they have recently been described by Asa Gray in Hooker's London Journal.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
